published in 1753.]

[Footnote 103: <i>Remembrancia</i>, vol. IX, p. 44.]

[Footnote 104: <i>The Great Trappaner of England Discovered</i>, p. 3.]

[Footnote 105: Violet's Petition, December 18, 1660, p. 1. The previous quotation is
from the Remonstrance concerning the Jews, November, 1660, <i>S. P. Dom.</i>
