No. 83.]

[Footnote 151: <i>S. P. Calendar</i>, Feb. 10, 1690.]

[Footnote 152: See Tovey's <i>Anglia Iudaica</i>, pp. 287-95.]

[Footnote 153: The <i>Commons Journals</i> give the numbers as 140 and 78. In reality no
